/*@ define:module:about_this_filter
---
name: About this filter
description: |
  This filter prioritizes readable text & reducing visual ground item clutter while saving the nice colors for the nice PVM drops. Unique drops colors are influenced by the boss they're from, otherwise ground item colors are based on their value with some special exceptions. 
    * This is version: 1.1
*/
meta { name = "ClearLoot"; }

/* #region  [1] do this first */
/*@ define:module:do_this_first
---
name: Settings
description: |
  1. On Runelite, click the wrench (configuration) on the side bar
  2. Search for the "Loot filters" plugin & go to the settings
  
    ### Plugin panel: 
    * Enabled [ **yes** ]

    ### General: 
    * Fetch default filters [ **no** ]
    * Show unmatched items [ **yes** ]
    * Ownership filter [ **no** ]
    * Item spawn filter [ **no** ]
    * Font mode [ **plugin** ]
    * Sound volume [ **100%** ]

    ### Hotkey
    * Hotkey:  [ **Alt** ]
    * Press: Show hidden items [ **yes** ]
    * Press: Show hide/ highlight box [ **yes** ]
    * Press: Show item values [ **no** ]
    * Double-tap: toggle overlay [ **yes** ]
    * Double-tap delay [ **250ms** ]

    ### Display settings	
    * Show value [ **no** ]
    * Value display [ **G.E** ]
    * Dual-value display [ **compact** ]
    * Show despawn [ **no** ]
    * Despawn type [ **seconds** ]
    * Despawn threshold [ **0 ticks** ]
    * Text accent [ **use filter** ]
    * Menu: collapse entries [ **no** ]
    * Menu: deprioritize hidden items [ **yes** ]
    * Menu: recolor hidden items [ **yes** ]
    * Hidden color [ **#808080** ]
    * Overlay priority [ **Low** ]
    * Overlay z -offset [ **16** ]

    ### Item lists
    * Highlight lootbeam [ **no** ]
    * Highlight notification [ **yes** ]
*/
/* #endregion */

/* #region [1] global rules*/
/*@ define:module:global_rules
---
name: Global Rules
description: |
    * Hidden + Clickable = 
    ground item have no text, but can be left-clicked
        * Write item names seperated by commas
    * Despawn timer = Hides the **timer** for items that cost less than
    * Show GE price = Hide item **prices** for items that cost less than
*/

/*@ define:input:global_rules
type: stringlist
label: Hidden + Clickable
*/
#define GLOBAL_HIDE []

apply (tradeable: true && name:"*") {
    hidden = true;
}

/*@ define:input:global_rules
type: number
label: Despawn timer - value
*/
#define GLOBAL_DESPAWN_HIDE 1200

/*@ define:input:global_rules
type: number
label: Show GE price - value
*/
#define GLOBAL_VALUE_HIDE 2000



apply (name:GLOBAL_HIDE) {
    hideOverlay = true;
}

apply (name:"*") {
    showDespawn = true;
}

apply (name:"*") {
    showValue = true;
}

apply (value:<GLOBAL_VALUE_HIDE) {
    showValue = false;
}

apply (value:>GLOBAL_VALUE_HIDE) {
    hidden = false;
}

/* #endregion */

/* #region [1] hidden items desc*/
/*@ define:module:hidden_items
---
name: Hidden Items
description: |
  - Stack Amount: 
    - Hides based on stack amount regardless of stack value
    - Non-noted items dont add up in "stack amount"

  - Stack Value: 
    - Hides based on stack value regardless of stack amount
    - Non-noted items dont add up in price
  
  - Others' Boat: 
    - Hides ground items in other people's boats

  - Boss Rooms: 
    - Hides ground items in boss rooms

  Ammo is under "Stack value" as to not get clutter of 1-2 bolts in minigames/wildy/slayer
*/
/* #endregion */

/* #region [1] hidden items */

/*@ define:input:hidden_items
type: stringlist
label: Less than 2
group: Stack amount
*/
